  <brief_title>Infrapyloric and Greater Curvature Lymph Node Metastasis in Colon Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Infrapyloric (No.206) and Greater Curvature (No.204) Lymph Node Metastasis in Adenocarcinoma Located at Hepatic Flexure and Right Half of Transverse Colon</official_title>
